<DocsPageTitle Path="Components/Time Edit">
    Blazorise TimeEdit component
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    A native time input component build around the <Code Tag>input type="time"</Code>.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

